I Drink Your Milkshake
{{needsmoar|shoops}}
{{spoiler|THE MILKSHAKE'S A LIEEEE!!!}}

[[Image:I-drink-your-milkshake-1.jpg|thumb|MILKSHAKE!]]
[[Image:Milkshake-awards.jpg‎|thumb|Daniel Day Lewis accepts his <s>Oscar</s> milkshake.]]
This dead on arrival '[[meme]]' originates from a scene in the Oscar winning movie ''There Will Be Blood'' starring Daniel Day Lewis, possibly [[2 girls 1 cup|the most epic movie ever]]. It is notable only for appearing a full [[slowpoke|''two years'']] after the movie came out, rendering it almost incomprehensible and only relevant to movie fanbois.

However, the scene that spawned it is probably one of the most epic movie scenes of all time complete with [[Some_argue|arguably]] the most awesome display of OTT overacting evar (this side of [[William Shatner]]) that won Daniel Day Lewis the Oscar for best actor in his turn as a batshit insane oilman in 1902. In the scene, Lewis' character, Daniel Plainview, is completely wasted on whiskey and 'explaining' to his arch nemesis, a fundie preacher called Eli Sunday, how all the oil (aka 'milkshake') on his neighbouring property [[pwnt|are belong to Plainview]] since his property's adjacent oil rigs are [[Rape|tapping]] the massive oil field which lays beneath both properties. The scene ends in an equally epic OTT fashion, when Plainview beats Eli to death with a [[Cock|bowling pin]] in his private bowling alley.

<center><youtube>dsQcS0zr4tM</youtube></center>

==YouTube==
[[Image:There will be blood0.jpg|thumb|left|250px|It is delicious milkshake...]]
[[Image:Milkshake12.19.03_PM.png|thumb|250px|...I will drink it up!]]
The scene has literally been molested to death all over YouTube with the most obvious remix being accompanied by R&B singer Kelis' song ''Milkshake''. Most however, have had the sound disabled thanks to the [[RIAA]]. The one remaining exception being this one.

